_sText:
jb_piranesi

Current version = jb_piranesi_beta_02c

Old project of mine, released privately on ]HeLL[ Clan. I've updated it to fix problems and decided to release it to the public. Enjoy, feedback appreciated. 

--Games--
  1. Cannon Game (Onto tower of boxes)
  2. Surf (From Cannon)
  3. Wipeout
  4. Jousting (CT v T | 1 on 1 | LR game)
  5. Traitor (Featuring ability to have 2 traitors at once)
  6. Dodgeball
  7. Climb
  8. Colours (Unique, with multiple squares of the same colour to run to)
  9. Disco with 6 songs
  10. Volleyball
  11. Deathcrate
  12. Football
  13. 4 Chairs (a.k.a 4 Corners)

--Features--
  • Armoury - ak47, m4a1, tmp, famas, awp, deagle, fiveseven, usp
  • Large Sewer system (a.k.a. Vent system)
  • Scout Secret
  • Hidden guns at various points around the map
